Three-Layer Safety Pipeline Architecture. Input Layer: Input Validation, PII Masking, Injection Detection, Length Checks. LLM Layer: System Prompt Hardening, Temperature 0.1, max_tokens Limit, RAG Context. Output Layer: Safety Check, Bias Detection, Factuality Check, PII Re-Check, Format Validation. Audit Log spans all layers. Horizontal layers, vertical audit line. Shield icons, German labels.